track_notes: Park at the entrance to Nant Ddu Farm on A4212(SH80573847)...room for one car..allow room for farm vehicles.Through entrance gate, then turn left shortly to follow Landrover track past Amnodd-bwll(derelict), turn right here and follow track up towards summit,when the track ends take a direct route towards summit.

Longer than Nant Ddu route but good for return via Arenig Fawr.
Park at start of track near the disused railway line on minor road. Same as my route to Arenig Fawr but keep straight on instead of turning up Craig y Hyrddod. Past the stile it is VERY wet. The lane has become a stream. Interesting ruins at SH 81603750 Amnodd-wen. Past here slight right onto forestry track. Another nice building at SH 80973688 Amnodd-bwll. Continue as per GW4VPX route. This took me 112 minutes.
